snippet: Ms. Cheney, the older daughter of former Vice President Dick Cheney, announced an intent to run, setting up a Republican primary clash next year that party officials had hoped to avoid.
abstract: Liz Cheney, oldest daughter of former Vice Pres Dick Cheney, announces that she intends to challenge Sen Michael B Enzi of Wyoming in a 2014 Republican primary clash that national and state party officials had hoped to avoid.
lead_paragraph: Ms. Cheney, the older daughter of former Vice President Dick Cheney, announced an intent to run, setting up a Republican primary clash next year that party officials had hoped to avoid.

headline.main: Liz Cheney to Challenge Senator Michael Enzi of Wyoming
